---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About Dr. Leonid Lurie',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="dl-section">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="dl-reading">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Dr. Leonid Lurie</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted">Let’s keep this simple.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
          If you’ve ever tried a health or skincare product that <em>promised everything</em>… and delivered very
          little—you’re not alone.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">And there’s a reason for that.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
          Most products focus on <strong>what’s inside the bottle</strong>. Dr. Leonid Lurie focuses on
          <strong>whether it actually works in your body</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="dl-card overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://kugelmedia.netlify.app/drlurieblog/dr-lurie-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Portrait of Dr. Leonid Lurie"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg"
          loading="lazy"
          onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
        />
        <div class="hidden items-center justify-center min-h-[360px] p-8 text-center text-muted">
          Portrait image unavailable
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">A Different Way of Thinking About Health</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">
        Dr. Lurie is a physician, scientist, and developer with more than 30 years of experience in medical and
        pharmaceutical research.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">But what makes his work different is this:</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">He doesn’t treat the body—especially the skin—as something passive.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">He sees it as a <strong>living, active system</strong>.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        And that changes everything. Because when you understand how the body really functions, you stop guessing… and
        start designing solutions that actually make a difference.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">Why Most Products Fall Short</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">Here’s the uncomfortable truth:</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        Even the best ingredients are useless if your body can’t absorb or use them properly.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        That’s why so many creams, treatments, and health products give <strong
          >temporary or disappointing results</strong
        >.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">Dr. Lurie built his career solving that exact problem.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">The Science Behind Real Results</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">
        Over decades of research, Dr. Lurie developed advanced delivery systems designed to help active ingredients:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Reach the right place in the body</li>
        <li>Work over time—not just for a few minutes</li>
        <li>Stay stable and effective</li>
        <li>Support the body without unnecessary stress</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">
        In practical terms, this means products that are designed to <strong>work with your body—not against it</strong
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">From Research to Real Life</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">This isn’t abstract science.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">Dr. Lurie’s work has been applied in areas such as:</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Skin health and aging</li>
        <li>Inflammation and healing</li>
        <li>Hygiene and long-lasting protection</li>
        <li>Professional-grade skincare used in clinics</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">
        The focus is always the same: <strong
          >Create solutions that people can actually use—and actually benefit from.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">Why This Blog Exists</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">This site isn’t here to overwhelm you with complex science.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">It’s here to help you:</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Better understand how your body works</li>
        <li>Make smarter decisions about products and treatments</li>
        <li>Avoid common mistakes that waste time and money</li>
        <li>Discover approaches grounded in real science—not marketing hype</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">
        Over time, you’ll also find carefully developed resources, products, and insights designed to support your
        health in a practical, realistic way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="dl-reading">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">A Personal Note</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted">After decades in research, Dr. Lurie has seen what works—and what doesn’t.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        This blog is a way to share that knowledge directly, without filters, trends, or shortcuts.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">Because when it comes to your health, you deserve more than promises.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
        <strong>You deserve solutions that make sense—and make a difference.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl font-medium">If that’s what you’re looking for, you’re in the right place.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dl-section border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Start With the Science</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted dl-reading">
      Explore how aging skin changes, why common approaches often fall short, and what a delivery-system approach makes
      possible.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <a class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto" href="/blog">Read the Insights</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto" href="/#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
